Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:06.33,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Düsseldorf Federation ・ Holding Cells
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:06.64,Default,,0,0,80,,Please ask Helene and Gustav for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask them to record "Detective Forster."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They show reruns Tuesday mornings at ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen here, Milch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how much trouble you caused the boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because you messed up and got caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even for an idiot like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he was kind enough to send someone\Nlike myself as your attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So show him some appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He only sent you to keep an eye on me, to\Nmake sure I didn't spill anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Milch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You do know what would happen\Nif you told the truth, don't you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sell out my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow my scenario and confess, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you already have the schedule\Nfor my next job figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you think that will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who should think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Gunther Milch, the Escape King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to waste on this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you confess like I told you, you'll\Nget out in about five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you tell them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Helene and Gustav to record\N"Detective Forster" for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but they're not really reliable...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should try that again while I'm still at this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Try what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:27.47,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1250,0)\pos(360,340)}Determination
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure he's not faking it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was blood in his vomit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and his body feels so cold so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't throw up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,keep an eye on this place for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, some new kids they brought\Nin went nuts on the third floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and I heard that some people were injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But this one looks like he's about to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You again, Milch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just put him on the bed in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look at him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Take me to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back, so just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, they keep bringing them in one after another today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be next to a serial killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why does it have to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got him on an I.V. drip because he\Ncollapsed after not eating anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel worse lying next to a guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and lie down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you said people were injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how many?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't know unless I go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make those kids pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,About what you said the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of killing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your former fiancée...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's a great idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she knows too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On that rainy day at the building under construction...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she heard three gunshots...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva would never testify about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She only wants me to be imprisoned for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All she thinks about is making\Nme regret leaving her forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll only testify to things that'll hurt me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked if it was a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you might not be sent to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Her death would be beneficial to both of us you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you tell the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will they believe a story like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you tell your attorney, Mr. Verdeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be one of my allies, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make sure you're found innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"We" being the excellent lawyers, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're free and you step outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll he able to have a nice drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, by then, that spoiled,\Nloud-mouthed, drunken bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be gone from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuck next to a murderer like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just stay silent to your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to confess and get transferred\Nto prison in the next five days!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it'll be goodbye to murderers like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you shouting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were faking it after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that felt good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to endure for five more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't be associated with killers like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In five days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, on that rainy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you heard three gunshots in a building\Nthat was under construction...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and saw a young, blonde man coming down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still plan on tackling this case\Nwhile denying Johan's existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have you present this important testimony in court?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:31.27,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\an8}Düsseldorf Federal Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.48,Default,,0,0,80,,What does Dr. Tenma want this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he mean, he has something\Nimportant he wants to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he just asked to see the investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In Düsseldorf... Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Director Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgical Director Oppenheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and my patient, Adolf Junkers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A gust of wind came...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The thermos fell over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The sandwiches were all dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,just sadly smiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to an announcement made by the police...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}early on the morning of the fourth...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the suspect Kenzo Tenma, who had consistently{\i}\N{\i1}denied involvement in a string of murders...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}completely reversed his position and confessed to{\i}\N{\i1}the murders of Eisler Memorial Hospital's director....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and two physicians in Düsseldorf....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as well as the murder of Adolf Junkers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has made a full confession.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This just came in.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}According to an announcement made by the police...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He confessed? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}early on the morning of the fourth...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the suspect, Kenzo Tenma, who had consistently{\i}\N{\i1}denied involvement in a string of murder cases....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has confessed to all of the charges against him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you guys do to Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of torture did you put him through\Nto squeeze that false confession out of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please let go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let me see Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to talk to him myself and have him tell me what\Nkind of treatment he received during his questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He even refused an interview with\Nme, and I'm his attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem that his confession was indeed voluntary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've looked into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the investigator myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a man who's capable of torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Tenma simply confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It went surprisingly smoothly, I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Verdeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you also believe his confession is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell what his intent is unless I interview him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Verdeman speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Baul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm terribly sorry for not being there at a time{\i}\N{\i1}like this, but I had to attend to an emergency.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, how was it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Dr. Tenma....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he refused my interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as we were trying really hard to prove his innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and have them drop the false charges...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he makes a full confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your father, on the other hand,{\i}\N{\i1}was quite an admirable person.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how grueling the interrogation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,he never faltered one step...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and continued to plead his innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His innocence...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what shall we do, Mr. Verdeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Verdeman?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That woman...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was her name again?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That important witness who can prove Tenma's innocence.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is she right now?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At a hotel in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I would certainly like to meet her in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a difficult woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I'll try meeting with her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was admirable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open the door, Miss Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The maids complained that they couldn't make the bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because you were in here drinking all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I fully understand that you hate Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If your relationship with Dr. Tenma had continued\Neven after you lost your father, the Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,your life would have been nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dr. Tenma left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that Dr. Tenma ruined your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was... imprisoned as a suspected spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For the longest time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was shunned, as the son of a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I also had my life ruined by my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I was able to keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believed in him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The people I believe in must be innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get Tenma's false charges dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma has to be innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My father had to have been innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My partner's and my contact information is written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us a call when you're ready to testify.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sending him to prison tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only been a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, it's because Tenma's{\i}\N{\i1}confession went so smoothly.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we do anything, Mr. Verdeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The police are also trying to convince{\i}\N{\i1}Tenma to meet with us, but...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the way, how is Miss Eva Heinemann?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably getting drunk at some bar again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Düsseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything looks so familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been sitting here for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really interesting paper, so I was copying it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you want to go somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:18:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how about French?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you keep writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay there and keep writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so, glad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Isn't it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If we put rocks down like this, the blanket\Nwon't blow away in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't talking, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking why you're spreading it out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice having lunch in a place like this once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather's nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Us, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I made some sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There are bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all dirty now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want one too, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Start walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get through to Mr. Verdeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, his wife just gave birth, so he's probably{\i}\N{\i1}still at the maternity center.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've heard about you, Miss Eva Heinemann.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, feel free to tell me anything you'd like.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About what?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The testimony to prove Tenma's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. We're very grateful!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what hotel are you staying at right now?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head over there right now.
